\f0\fs24 \cf0 \'93Well, that was rude,\'94 said Grundy. \'93Anyway, I understand the Grimmer Company runs a number of newspapers and literary magazines, isn't that right? Quite a business, I imagine.\'94
\f1\fs20 \

\f0\fs24 \'93We also publish penny dreadfuls,\'94 Jonathan said with a grin, enjoying the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://CE0A4284-FAEA-44F8-9126-0C7E28A6CD83"}}{\fldrslt look}} on Grundy's face. Meanwhile, Miss Karnstein\'92s eyes lit up.
