\f0\fs24 The last conversation he\'92d had with his father, they\'92d talked about Jonathan taking on more responsibilities with the company. \cb2 Now that his father was gone, he had a nagging sense of guilt about everything. He wished he\'92d spent more time with his father. At least it wasn\'92t too late to start taking an interest in the company\cb1 .
